# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supabase — dev project (gitignored; safe to keep secrets here)
# Find these in the Supabase dashboard for your dev project:
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL       Project Settings -> Data API -> Project URL
#                           (or https://<project-ref>.supabase.co)
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  Project Settings -> API Keys -> anon / public
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# NOTE: the service-role key is NOT used by the frontend and must never live in
# a VITE_* var (those ship to the browser). It goes into edge-function secrets
# later via: npx supabase secrets set SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=...
